<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 27 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />终于到钓鱼大赛的日子啦，<delay20 />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />从早上开始我就超紧张的！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 27 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果你感觉非常喜欢<delay8 />钓起的鱼，<delay20 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />也可以直接把它养起来哦～！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 27 00 00 00 00"><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今天我可要好好享受<delay8 />
这次钓鱼大赛哦～！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但要是我一条都钓不到，那该怎么办呢～<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />还好，<delay8 />每次我
差不多要放弃的时候，<delay20 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />总会突然就钓上鱼来的！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />人家说钓鱼讲究的是时机，<delay20 />
<anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />可是要钓上鱼来，<delay8 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我觉得还是需要一些运气的！<pageBreak /><anim id="Hesitate" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以我每天早上<delay20 />先做星相占卜，
确认好当天的运势之后<delay8 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />才决定要不要出门钓鱼哦～！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要参加钓鱼大赛的话，<delay20 />
